llercoaster rides or at scary horror movies. Not that rollercoaster rides and scary movies didn''t make her want to. But she just controlled the urge. Always. So she didn''t even realize that was her screaming at the top of her lungs for a second or two.', 23978, 0), (349326, 'Cassie - She loved reading romances - contemporary stuff. She wasn''t into fantasy. No fairytale princess and prince stories. No vampires. No werewolves. No immortal fae.', 23978, 0), (349327, 'Be careful, darling. Your footsteps land heavy here. Your racket will wake the dragons.', 308, 0), (349328, 'If dragons were real, then in all likelihood they were not graceful, high-chested, noble creatures; rather they would have been dirty, ugly, reptilian and mean.', 9534, 0), (349329, 'The man who fights too long against dragons becomes a dragon himself.', 11, 0), (349330, 'Dragons think we are amusing. But they remember Erreth-Akbe. They speak of him as if he were a dragon, not a man.', 77, 0), (349331, 'Her dark eyes slid to him. "I can''t remember the last time I felt so good in clothes."And he wanted to get her out of them.', 35879, 0), (349332, 'You''ve walked the woods today. Tell me there isna something about this land that doesna take hold of you and sink into your verra soul."Her smile slowly faded. "It did. How did you know?""You were born here, Iona.You were part of this land, just as it''s a part of you. You''ve been gone a long time, but it still remembers you. You just needed to remember it.', 35879, 0), (349333, 'An enemy is always an enemy, even when they''re an ally." - Taraeth', 35879, 0), (349334, 'Azdaha were no joke. ... Not much is known about this dragon [the aforementioned Gandarw], except that he apparently had yellow heels. I wonder why that was such an important detail. I mean if I were describing Godzilla, the color of his heels wouldn’t be the first thing I would mention.', 762, 0), (349335, 'A memory, long buried, sprang up of her father warning her never to cross the 